@startuml S9 - Log-in dan Log-out

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

actor Mahasiswa
actor Dosen
participant "S9. Auth" as Auth
database "DB: User" as DBUser

== Login Mahasiswa ==

Mahasiswa -> Auth : Login (NIM, PASSWORD)
Auth -> DBUser : Cari user berdasarkan nomorInduk
DBUser --> Auth : Data user + role
Auth -> Auth : Validasi password (bcrypt)
Auth --> Mahasiswa : Token JWT + data user (role: MAHASISWA)

== Login Dosen ==

Dosen -> Auth : Login (NIP, PASSWORD)
Auth -> DBUser : Cari user berdasarkan nomorInduk
DBUser --> Auth : Data user + role
Auth -> Auth : Validasi password (bcrypt)
Auth --> Dosen : Token JWT + data user (role: DOSEN)

== Akses Endpoint Terproteksi ==

Mahasiswa -> Auth : Request + Authorization: Bearer <token>
Auth -> Auth : Verifikasi token JWT
Auth --> Mahasiswa : Lanjut ke proses yang dituju

== Log-out ==

Mahasiswa -> Auth : Logout
Auth --> Mahasiswa : Hapus token di client (localStorage)

Dosen -> Auth : Logout
Auth --> Dosen : Hapus token di client (localStorage)

@enduml
